WEBVTT

01:42.640 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:16.280 --> 02:17.360
Are you done?

02:22.720 --> 02:23.880
I'm going to wash the towel.

02:42.200 --> 02:44.040
Why didn't he give me a heads-up

02:45.360 --> 02:46.920
before he opened his eyes?

02:47.560 --> 02:48.880
He could've said,

02:49.800 --> 02:51.280
"I'm going to open my eyes,"

02:51.360 --> 02:52.640
and then opened them.

02:54.320 --> 02:55.520
He suddenly opened them.

02:56.800 --> 02:57.840
What the heck?

03:02.040 --> 03:03.160
He gave me a scare.

03:35.520 --> 03:36.360
Are you done?

03:38.160 --> 03:39.160
Jiaxu.

03:40.360 --> 03:42.320
I think you should get some rest.

03:42.400 --> 03:43.680
Leave work for tomorrow.

03:43.760 --> 03:44.960
Okay, in a bit.

04:02.760 --> 04:04.760
Sorry, Sang Zhi.

04:04.840 --> 04:06.680
You came all this way to suffer with me.

04:09.160 --> 04:10.040
I don't mind.

04:11.840 --> 04:12.880
Don't move.

04:12.960 --> 04:14.000
I can handle it.

04:16.720 --> 04:17.720
I'll turn the lights off.

04:18.320 --> 04:19.160
Okay.

04:25.560 --> 04:26.440
Here.

04:27.640 --> 04:28.960
Use this pillow.

04:30.920 --> 04:32.040
My clothes are over there.

04:32.120 --> 04:33.200
Cover yourself with them

04:33.280 --> 04:34.200
so you don't get cold.

04:42.120 --> 04:42.960
Let's sleep.

05:25.920 --> 05:27.120
WEIWEI

05:27.200 --> 05:28.120
THE OTHER PARTY HAS CANCELED

05:28.200 --> 05:29.400
DORM 202 GIRLS' GROUP

05:29.480 --> 05:31.640
SANGSANG, ARE YOU OKAY?

05:31.720 --> 05:32.960
CONTACT US WHEN YOU SEE THIS.

05:33.040 --> 05:33.920
SANGSANG, ARE YOU OKAY?

05:36.000 --> 05:37.600
I'M HERE

05:37.680 --> 05:39.440
I have a brother…

05:50.160 --> 05:51.680
I have a relative

05:52.560 --> 05:53.400
who is ill.

05:54.200 --> 05:55.800
I won't be coming back tonight.

05:55.880 --> 05:56.840
Don't worry about me.

05:56.920 --> 05:58.280
JIANG MING

06:00.280 --> 06:02.920
Sang Zhi, I'm outside the theater.

06:03.000 --> 06:04.000
Are you here yet?

06:19.880 --> 06:20.760
You can't sleep?

06:25.920 --> 06:28.080
Do you need to finish listening
to the voice message?

06:32.120 --> 06:34.560
Jiaxu, why did you pretend to be asleep?

06:36.080 --> 06:37.440
I was just quiet.

06:38.040 --> 06:39.240
I didn't pretend to be asleep.

06:39.320 --> 06:40.600
That is pretending to be asleep.

06:41.440 --> 06:43.160
You were even eavesdropping.

06:43.800 --> 06:44.760
Eavesdropping?

06:47.040 --> 06:48.640
You're the one who played the message.

06:48.720 --> 06:51.200
You're making false claims
at such a young age.

06:54.800 --> 06:56.040
I'm not talking to you anymore.

06:56.760 --> 06:58.280
I'm going to sleep. Good night.

07:03.560 --> 07:04.480
Can you fall asleep?

07:10.680 --> 07:11.960
It's time for bed either way.

07:13.840 --> 07:14.760
Come on.

07:16.160 --> 07:17.320
Chat with me.

07:28.680 --> 07:29.840
About what?

07:30.880 --> 07:32.400
Finish playing that voice message.

07:33.360 --> 07:34.400
Let me see

07:35.080 --> 07:37.280
who wants to ask you out to a movie.

07:40.160 --> 07:41.440
You don't know him.

07:43.040 --> 07:44.880
I will once you tell me about him.

07:45.440 --> 07:46.560
I'll judge him for you.

07:47.640 --> 07:49.720
Why? We're just going to the movies.

07:51.520 --> 07:53.760
I'm just worried you're naïve
and might get played.

07:56.240 --> 07:57.480
Well, I could spend all night

07:58.520 --> 07:59.880
talking about guys.

07:59.960 --> 08:01.320
There are so many of them.

08:06.080 --> 08:09.080
Our Sang Zhi is so popular.

08:12.880 --> 08:13.960
It's because I'm pretty.

08:29.760 --> 08:32.960
Why isn't he saying anything?

08:38.720 --> 08:39.600
Jiaxu.

08:41.000 --> 08:42.120
Look.

08:42.200 --> 08:44.120
People your age should be asleep

08:44.200 --> 08:45.640
at this hour.

08:47.080 --> 08:50.400
Don't always try to pry
into the lives of young people.

08:50.920 --> 08:53.160
You don't understand our world.

08:53.240 --> 08:54.400
You won't get it

08:54.480 --> 08:56.120
even if I tell you about it.

09:01.200 --> 09:02.040
Fine.

09:03.040 --> 09:04.320
I don't know anything.

10:22.840 --> 10:23.720
It's all done.

10:24.880 --> 10:26.000
Thank you, Sang Zhi.

10:31.880 --> 10:34.560
Jiaxu, I'm going to class.

10:35.560 --> 10:37.640
Let me know if you need anything.

10:37.720 --> 10:38.840
I'll bring it tonight.

10:38.920 --> 10:40.160
Perfect.

10:40.800 --> 10:42.240
Go to my place

10:42.320 --> 10:44.720
and get my laptop from my study.

10:44.800 --> 10:46.280
The keys are in my jacket pocket.

10:46.360 --> 10:48.360
I'll send you the address later.

10:50.160 --> 10:51.480
What do you need the laptop for?

10:52.320 --> 10:53.400
For work, of course.

10:54.800 --> 10:56.640
But you're ill.

10:56.720 --> 10:58.280
You should focus on resting.

10:58.360 --> 10:59.800
Even if you do your work now,

11:00.320 --> 11:01.760
your boss won't pay you extra.

11:03.040 --> 11:04.800
It's too bad. I live for tech.

11:10.920 --> 11:11.840
Got it.

11:12.680 --> 11:14.680
But I still won't bring the laptop over.

11:14.760 --> 11:16.120
I'll take care of the rest.

11:25.920 --> 11:26.800
What's wrong?

11:29.000 --> 11:30.480
Hearing you lecture me

11:31.280 --> 11:32.400
makes me realize

11:32.480 --> 11:33.880
that our Sang Zhi has grown up.

11:38.920 --> 11:40.040
I am a grown-up.

11:42.400 --> 11:43.840
I'm not a kid anymore.

11:46.800 --> 11:48.040
Did you just realize that?

11:52.400 --> 11:53.320
I'm off.

12:01.240 --> 12:03.440
CHAPTER TEN, JOKE

12:03.520 --> 12:05.560
GIVE ME A REASON TO FORGET

12:08.720 --> 12:09.720
I'm here. Where are you?

12:09.800 --> 12:11.680
Here.

12:11.760 --> 12:12.800
I see you.

12:14.760 --> 12:15.920
Good morning, students.

12:16.000 --> 12:17.040
We meet again.

12:17.840 --> 12:19.040
Where were you?

12:21.880 --> 12:22.800
I can't believe you.

12:22.880 --> 12:24.000
I brought you breakfast.

12:24.080 --> 12:24.960
Eat it later.

12:25.880 --> 12:26.720
Thank you.

12:27.200 --> 12:29.120
How is your relative?

12:29.920 --> 12:31.520
He's done with his surgery.

12:31.600 --> 12:32.720
I think

12:32.800 --> 12:34.280
he should be discharged in a few days.

12:34.360 --> 12:35.760
I'll visit him after class.

12:35.840 --> 12:37.200
Again?

12:37.280 --> 12:38.560
Are you going to accompany him?

12:39.680 --> 12:41.320
Well, I have to do it.

12:41.400 --> 12:42.520
I'm also in Yihe.

12:42.600 --> 12:44.200
I can't push it off to someone else.

12:46.960 --> 12:49.120
Jiang Ming was disappointed
that you didn't show up

12:49.200 --> 12:50.320
and kept asking about you.

12:51.080 --> 12:52.960
Chen Qiang told me about the tickets.

12:53.040 --> 12:54.000
- They--
- Ning Wei.

12:55.480 --> 12:58.240
Okay, the homework I assigned last week
is due today.

12:58.320 --> 12:59.320
Have you completed it?

12:59.400 --> 13:00.520
The tickets were hard to get.

13:03.360 --> 13:05.560
Two, two, three, four.

13:05.640 --> 13:07.720
Five, six, seven, eight.

13:07.800 --> 13:10.560
Three, two, three, four.

13:10.640 --> 13:13.120
- Sang Zhi!
- Five, six, seven, eight.

13:13.200 --> 13:15.640
Four, two, three, four.

13:15.720 --> 13:17.840
Five, six, seven. Stop.

13:18.720 --> 13:19.640
Good morning.

13:20.320 --> 13:21.280
You have sharp eyes.

13:23.200 --> 13:25.280
Right, why didn't you join us

13:25.760 --> 13:27.080
for the movie yesterday?

13:29.520 --> 13:31.480
My relative suddenly fell ill yesterday.

13:31.560 --> 13:33.160
I was taking care of him at the hospital.

13:33.880 --> 13:35.080
Is he all right now?

13:35.160 --> 13:36.200
He's fine now.

13:38.160 --> 13:41.040
I'm sorry I couldn't make it.

13:41.120 --> 13:43.480
But we can catch a movie some other time

13:43.560 --> 13:44.520
when you're free.

13:45.240 --> 13:46.200
Sure.

13:46.280 --> 13:48.920
I'm free next weekend.

13:51.000 --> 13:51.880
Well,

13:52.880 --> 13:55.360
I'll treat you to a movie next weekend.

13:56.160 --> 13:58.160
Okay, then I'll see you next weekend.

14:02.800 --> 14:05.120
Yes. I'm going to warm up now.

14:05.680 --> 14:06.840
- Bye.
- Bye.

14:15.120 --> 14:16.160
122 ABNORMALITIES

14:17.960 --> 14:19.120
67.5 ABNORMALITIES

14:26.520 --> 14:28.000
Then the characters are projected

14:28.080 --> 14:30.440
- and the whole scene will--
- Hold on.

14:33.760 --> 14:34.640
Hello, Jiaxu?

14:35.520 --> 14:36.720
Hi, Siyun.

14:36.800 --> 14:39.000
The logic in this part is too wordy.

14:39.080 --> 14:40.440
The program won't run.

14:41.000 --> 14:43.040
I don't have a computer with me right now.

14:43.120 --> 14:44.120
Can you have someone

14:44.200 --> 14:45.720
bring me one from the office?

14:45.800 --> 14:46.920
I'll code this bit.

14:47.000 --> 14:48.000
It's okay.

14:48.080 --> 14:49.280
Focus on recovering.

14:50.000 --> 14:52.640
I'll have them handle
the other parts first.

14:52.720 --> 14:53.760
It's fine.

14:53.840 --> 14:55.840
I have nothing to do here anyway.

14:57.320 --> 14:58.440
Jiaxu.

14:58.520 --> 15:02.000
If your wound opens up again,

15:02.080 --> 15:03.480
who is going to work for me?

15:03.560 --> 15:04.520
Rest well.

15:33.880 --> 15:38.720
JIANG YING

15:38.800 --> 15:43.920
VOICE MESSAGE FROM JIANG YING

15:44.000 --> 15:44.920
I'm sorry.

15:45.000 --> 15:47.080
I know I was too emotional.

15:48.920 --> 15:51.000
I'm sorry. I really will change this time.

15:51.840 --> 15:53.440
I will control myself from now on.

16:17.880 --> 16:19.440
Number 158.

18:28.680 --> 18:30.160
Both of you look at the camera.

18:45.240 --> 18:46.840
This must be his mom.

18:47.800 --> 18:48.920
Nice to meet you.

18:49.000 --> 18:49.920
I am Sang Zhi.

19:36.640 --> 19:37.600
I think

19:38.920 --> 19:40.880
he will need underwear.

20:34.080 --> 20:35.240
Wait!

20:35.320 --> 20:36.520
I'm going inside.

20:36.600 --> 20:37.880
Thank you.

20:56.040 --> 20:58.440
Jiaxu, it's me, Jiang Ying.

21:02.600 --> 21:03.440
Jiaxu?

21:08.240 --> 21:09.520
Jiaxu, are you home?

21:10.200 --> 21:11.120
Open up!

21:31.520 --> 21:32.360
Jiaxu.

21:51.680 --> 21:52.520
You're here.

21:52.600 --> 21:54.280
I didn't know you were in the bathroom.

21:54.360 --> 21:55.520
It's okay. I can do it myself.

21:58.520 --> 22:00.920
An old man has occupied the other bed.

22:03.320 --> 22:04.920
He went downstairs for a stroll.

22:11.000 --> 22:11.840
Hot water.

22:11.920 --> 22:13.360
- Thank you.
- Careful, it's hot.

22:16.600 --> 22:17.920
You brought a lot of stuff.

22:18.760 --> 22:19.720
It's not that much.

22:20.360 --> 22:21.400
Two sets of clothes.

22:22.120 --> 22:23.840
One is for when you're discharged.

22:23.920 --> 22:25.600
The other can keep you…

22:37.480 --> 22:39.280
Also,

22:39.360 --> 22:41.320
I brought the stuff you wanted.

22:47.920 --> 22:48.800
Thank you.

22:53.680 --> 22:54.560
Jiaxu.

22:56.520 --> 22:58.440
Don't stay up too late working.

22:58.520 --> 22:59.680
You're still recovering.

23:00.280 --> 23:02.400
Okay, I promise you.

23:03.040 --> 23:04.880
Screens off at 10:00 p.m. sharp.

23:08.160 --> 23:09.400
One hour left.

23:17.640 --> 23:18.480
Hello.

23:18.560 --> 23:19.920
- Hello.
- Hello.

23:23.480 --> 23:24.640
Have you eaten?

23:24.720 --> 23:26.440
- Here.
- Sit.

23:26.520 --> 23:28.160
Not yet. I'll have dinner later.

23:28.240 --> 23:29.520
Not yet?

23:30.240 --> 23:31.920
- Sit.
- It's already past eight.

23:32.000 --> 23:33.440
I'm not hungry yet.

23:33.520 --> 23:35.640
Stop putting away things.
Go and eat dinner.

23:35.720 --> 23:36.920
In a bit.

23:38.480 --> 23:40.080
I'll order delivery for you.

23:46.040 --> 23:47.440
I went to get your things

23:47.520 --> 23:49.000
right after I finished class.

23:49.080 --> 23:50.440
I haven't even sat down yet,

23:50.520 --> 23:51.760
but you keep telling me to eat.

23:51.840 --> 23:54.360
Why do you keep telling me to eat?

23:57.120 --> 23:58.240
Boy,

23:58.800 --> 23:59.800
is this your wife?

24:03.560 --> 24:04.440
Sir.

24:04.520 --> 24:06.640
How did you come to the conclusion
that she is my wife?

24:07.720 --> 24:09.200
She's beautiful.

24:09.760 --> 24:11.320
- Here, Dad.
- Okay.

24:11.400 --> 24:12.520
Thank you.

24:12.600 --> 24:13.440
Sir,

24:13.520 --> 24:14.680
this is my sister,

24:14.760 --> 24:15.840
not my wife.

24:17.320 --> 24:19.160
I know your wife is pretty.

24:20.760 --> 24:21.640
Sorry,

24:21.720 --> 24:24.520
my dad is hard of hearing.

24:25.440 --> 24:27.840
Dad, that's his sister,

24:27.920 --> 24:29.520
not his wife.

24:29.600 --> 24:32.240
A brother cannot marry his sister.

24:33.640 --> 24:35.240
Are you two not married yet?

24:39.520 --> 24:40.720
Boy,

24:40.800 --> 24:42.520
you don't look young anymore.

24:42.600 --> 24:44.040
Why aren't you married yet?

24:44.120 --> 24:46.800
Don't keep the young lady waiting.

24:47.640 --> 24:48.480
Sir.

24:49.120 --> 24:50.640
Please stop making me laugh.

24:50.720 --> 24:51.920
I have a wound on my stomach.

24:52.000 --> 24:55.200
Boy, I'm not joking.

24:55.920 --> 24:57.240
You need to get a move on.

24:57.320 --> 24:59.080
Your wife is pretty

24:59.160 --> 25:00.680
and so caring.

25:00.760 --> 25:01.680
Look at her

25:01.760 --> 25:03.640
carrying all these bags here.

25:03.720 --> 25:05.720
You must cherish her

25:05.800 --> 25:08.560
or else, you'll regret it later.

25:08.640 --> 25:10.520
Okay, I understand.

25:15.920 --> 25:17.680
He has poor hearing.

25:17.760 --> 25:18.760
Don't mind him.

25:18.840 --> 25:20.320
Just think of it as a joke.

25:22.520 --> 25:23.840
A joke?

25:24.800 --> 25:26.880
You shouldn't joke about these things.

25:31.720 --> 25:32.640
Sir.

25:33.320 --> 25:34.680
He is not my partner.

25:35.920 --> 25:37.720
He is too old

25:37.800 --> 25:38.960
to be my partner.

25:39.440 --> 25:40.840
He is old enough to be my dad.

25:43.800 --> 25:45.200
It's great to be a dad!

25:45.880 --> 25:47.240
Once you two get married,

25:47.320 --> 25:48.840
hurry up and have a child.

25:49.920 --> 25:51.120
You'll settle down.

25:51.200 --> 25:53.280
That is more important than anything.

26:07.440 --> 26:08.480
I'm going to go eat.

26:11.360 --> 26:12.320
Eat more.

26:12.400 --> 26:13.440
Order more.

26:14.240 --> 26:15.640
Why is your wife leaving?

26:17.360 --> 26:19.320
My wife is going to eat.

26:19.400 --> 26:20.280
To dinner.

26:22.120 --> 26:23.800
That's not something to joke about.

26:51.520 --> 26:52.640
Jiaxu.

26:53.760 --> 26:54.880
Good morning.

26:54.960 --> 26:56.720
Don't tell me you worked all night.

27:00.520 --> 27:02.120
I shouldn't have brought you the laptop.

27:06.880 --> 27:08.080
Jiaxu.

27:08.160 --> 27:09.680
You've been hospitalized.

27:09.760 --> 27:11.320
Why won't you just rest?

27:11.400 --> 27:13.400
Do you really think you are Superman?

27:14.640 --> 27:16.520
You've discovered my hidden identity.

27:16.600 --> 27:18.360
What hidden identity?

27:18.440 --> 27:20.000
How could you stay up all night?

27:20.080 --> 27:22.160
Are you having a lovers' spat so early?

27:22.240 --> 27:23.400
When is the wedding?

27:23.880 --> 27:25.080
Sir,

27:25.160 --> 27:26.240
we're not like that.

27:26.320 --> 27:27.320
We're not getting married.

27:27.400 --> 27:29.160
Are you not getting married?

27:29.640 --> 27:30.960
That won't do!

27:31.440 --> 27:32.480
She's a beautiful girl

27:32.560 --> 27:34.200
and she is taking care of you.

27:34.280 --> 27:35.920
How can you do this to her?

27:37.760 --> 27:39.240
Okay, we'll do as you say.

27:39.320 --> 27:40.240
We'll get married.

27:40.320 --> 27:41.760
That's more like it.

27:41.840 --> 27:43.160
You two are a perfect match.

27:43.240 --> 27:44.800
You will be happy together.

27:46.280 --> 27:47.280
I'll get you some water.

27:48.080 --> 27:50.680
Sir, she's too young.

27:50.760 --> 27:51.920
She's not of legal age yet.

27:52.000 --> 27:53.600
- Stop this joke.
- Maybe in two years.

27:54.760 --> 27:57.680
OUTPATIENT BUILDING

28:02.800 --> 28:04.000
Are you discharged?

28:04.840 --> 28:05.760
That's right, sir.

28:06.720 --> 28:09.680
Please rest well and recover soon.

28:10.240 --> 28:12.720
All right. You two get along now, okay?

28:14.080 --> 28:15.120
- Sir.
- We will, sir.

28:16.120 --> 28:17.720
We'll get married soon.

28:17.800 --> 28:19.680
That's good!

28:19.760 --> 28:21.000
Get well soon.

28:22.520 --> 28:23.560
Take care of each other.

28:24.520 --> 28:25.920
- Get along.
- Let's go.

28:29.840 --> 28:30.720
We're leaving, sir.

28:31.320 --> 28:32.200
Stay together.

28:40.080 --> 28:41.240
"We'll get married soon"?

28:44.720 --> 28:46.520
You're the one who started this joke.

28:49.160 --> 28:50.520
- I'll get that.
- I've told you.

28:50.600 --> 28:52.080
I'll carry it.

28:56.000 --> 28:56.920
Are you really upset?

29:00.160 --> 29:02.280
Don't make jokes like that anymore.

29:04.520 --> 29:05.600
Well,

29:06.120 --> 29:07.880
I've been in the hospital for so long.

29:07.960 --> 29:09.200
I was bored.

29:09.280 --> 29:10.240
I apologize.

29:12.000 --> 29:13.720
Does being bored make it okay

29:13.800 --> 29:15.160
to make jokes at my expense?

29:16.000 --> 29:17.080
You're unbelievable.

29:29.120 --> 29:30.360
You can wear my slippers.

29:32.120 --> 29:33.320
I'll take that.

29:33.400 --> 29:34.960
It's okay. I've got it.

29:39.800 --> 29:40.880
Take a seat.

29:40.960 --> 29:41.960
What do you want to drink?

29:44.360 --> 29:45.320
I'm fine.

29:50.480 --> 29:51.320
No need to tidy up.

29:51.400 --> 29:52.400
I'll do it later.

29:53.600 --> 29:55.800
Let's have dinner together later.

29:55.880 --> 29:57.120
I'll see you off after that.

30:00.360 --> 30:01.600
I'm going to use the bathroom.

30:19.240 --> 30:21.320
When I heard your brother say

30:21.400 --> 30:23.040
that you were coming here for university,

30:24.160 --> 30:25.040
I was really happy.

30:47.920 --> 30:51.160
The feelings that I've been hiding

30:51.240 --> 30:53.400
for the past two years

30:55.920 --> 30:57.120
probably

30:58.160 --> 30:59.720
don't mean the same to him.

31:00.400 --> 31:01.800
How old can you be?

31:01.880 --> 31:03.360
You're still a kid.

31:03.440 --> 31:05.160
Come when you don't have classes.

31:05.880 --> 31:07.520
I'm an adult.

31:07.600 --> 31:09.440
Don't trouble yourself for me.

31:10.280 --> 31:12.920
Sir, she's too young.

31:13.000 --> 31:14.600
She's not of legal age yet.

31:14.680 --> 31:15.720
Maybe in two years.

31:16.280 --> 31:17.960
He has poor hearing.

31:18.040 --> 31:19.120
Don't mind him.

31:19.200 --> 31:20.400
Just think of it as a joke.

31:21.880 --> 31:23.440
Maybe in his heart,

31:24.640 --> 31:27.400
we'll never be anything
more than brother and sister.

31:28.880 --> 31:31.320
That's why he can make jokes like that.

32:00.240 --> 32:03.600
TAKE THE MEDICINE ON TIME

32:03.680 --> 32:07.440
TAKE THE MEDICINE ON TIME

32:15.680 --> 32:16.800
What are you writing?

32:19.080 --> 32:19.920
Jiaxu.

32:20.680 --> 32:23.120
You need to pay attention to your diet.

32:23.200 --> 32:24.920
You can't have milk or eggs.

32:26.000 --> 32:28.080
But you can eat foods high in fiber

32:28.160 --> 32:29.360
to promote digestion.

32:32.000 --> 32:34.120
Also, try not to sit for too long

32:35.000 --> 32:36.200
while you work.

32:36.280 --> 32:38.680
Get up and walk around for a bit.

32:39.920 --> 32:42.280
But no strenuous exercise.

32:42.360 --> 32:44.040
Don't carry heavy items either.

32:44.120 --> 32:45.000
And…

32:56.480 --> 32:57.560
No staying up late.

32:58.320 --> 33:00.240
I know. Take a break.

33:05.000 --> 33:07.400
Stay home and recuperate
for the time being.

33:07.480 --> 33:09.760
If there is anything you need to buy,

33:09.840 --> 33:10.800
you can tell me.

33:10.880 --> 33:11.920
I'll get them for you.

33:13.360 --> 33:14.360
After this,

33:15.480 --> 33:18.440
I have a lot of assignments to complete.

33:18.520 --> 33:20.440
I need to go back and work on them,

33:21.120 --> 33:23.520
so I might not be coming over as often.

33:26.520 --> 33:27.640
One more thing.

33:29.280 --> 33:30.200
You…

33:31.360 --> 33:32.800
I want to treat you to a meal.

33:32.880 --> 33:34.000
We can wait

33:34.520 --> 33:35.920
until you have recovered.

33:36.600 --> 33:37.760
You don't have to do that.

33:37.840 --> 33:39.320
I should be the one treating you now.

33:42.920 --> 33:44.000
Okay.

33:44.560 --> 33:46.640
We'll talk about it later.

33:48.200 --> 33:49.400
I'm leaving.

33:49.480 --> 33:50.360
I'll send you off.

33:50.440 --> 33:51.280
It's okay, Jiaxu.

33:51.360 --> 33:53.200
- I'll go by myself.
- I'll take you to the metro.

33:53.280 --> 33:54.280
You don't have to do that.

33:56.280 --> 33:58.000
I can go back on my own.

33:59.120 --> 34:00.480
Bye, Jiaxu.

34:22.280 --> 34:23.600
This is fine.

34:24.520 --> 34:25.440
After all,

34:26.760 --> 34:28.320
I'm just his little sister.

34:34.719 --> 34:35.840
JIAXU

34:36.480 --> 34:37.880
REMARK: JIAXU

34:42.880 --> 34:45.679
EDIT CONTACT DETAILS

34:45.760 --> 34:48.120
BROTHER NO. 2

35:18.360 --> 35:20.160
NO STAYING UP LATE

36:03.000 --> 36:05.560
THAT'S A LITTLE DIFFICULT

36:05.640 --> 36:07.000
EAT ON TIME

36:07.080 --> 36:09.400
I'VE EATEN

36:14.840 --> 36:16.040
NO MILK OR EGGS

36:16.120 --> 36:17.200
EAT FOODS HIGH IN FIBER

36:17.280 --> 36:18.440
DON'T SIT FOR TOO LONG

36:18.520 --> 36:19.480
GET UP AND MOVE, BYE

37:02.560 --> 37:04.560
THE DREAM GAMES

37:05.120 --> 37:06.200
So is that what happened?

37:10.440 --> 37:12.600
I think she might really be upset.

37:13.640 --> 37:14.800
But I can't figure out

37:15.280 --> 37:16.720
the reason.

37:17.320 --> 37:18.480
What's the big deal?

37:18.560 --> 37:20.360
All you did was make a few jokes

37:20.440 --> 37:21.640
to go along with that old man.

37:23.120 --> 37:24.760
Siyun, what do you think?

37:25.920 --> 37:28.040
What goes on in men's heads?

37:28.600 --> 37:29.800
She's a girl.

37:29.880 --> 37:31.960
It's normal for a girl to be upset.

37:32.040 --> 37:33.280
Think about it.

37:33.360 --> 37:36.520
You said she has always been prideful

37:36.600 --> 37:37.480
and thin-skinned.

37:37.560 --> 37:39.400
You joked about her relationship status.

37:39.480 --> 37:40.560
Of course she would be mad.

37:41.520 --> 37:42.800
You even said

37:43.320 --> 37:45.080
she had a boy she liked.

37:45.160 --> 37:46.760
That would surely make her even angrier.

37:47.360 --> 37:48.840
I'm not the one who made the joke.

37:48.920 --> 37:50.000
It was that old man.

37:50.600 --> 37:52.880
She's taking it out on me.

37:52.960 --> 37:54.280
You're clearly an accomplice.

37:54.920 --> 37:56.080
She took care of you.

37:56.680 --> 37:58.720
But you and the old man joked about her.

37:58.800 --> 38:00.200
You're lucky she took care of you

38:00.280 --> 38:01.720
until you were discharged.

38:03.480 --> 38:06.760
I only wanted to indulge the old man.

38:06.840 --> 38:08.840
It's all the same to her. All right?

38:09.440 --> 38:10.800
Let me interrupt you guys.

38:11.520 --> 38:13.800
Did you call Siyun and me over

38:13.880 --> 38:15.760
just because of this problem?

38:16.480 --> 38:17.840
This is such a petty matter.

38:18.400 --> 38:19.520
I thought you had

38:19.600 --> 38:21.160
actual relationship problems.

38:21.240 --> 38:23.600
You had best pray that I don't.

38:23.680 --> 38:25.480
Who else will help you
with the game expansion?

38:25.560 --> 38:26.920
Well, thank you.

38:29.080 --> 38:29.960
How about this?

38:30.480 --> 38:31.360
Find some time

38:31.440 --> 38:32.520
and take her out for a meal.

38:32.600 --> 38:33.840
Talk things through with her

38:33.920 --> 38:35.200
and it should be fine.

38:35.280 --> 38:38.080
Also, you should be more careful.

38:38.160 --> 38:39.640
She's an adult now.

38:39.720 --> 38:42.200
You can't joke
about everything like before.

38:42.920 --> 38:43.920
Got it.

38:44.000 --> 38:45.240
Siyun is right.

38:45.720 --> 38:46.720
End of counseling.

38:46.800 --> 38:47.680
Get back to work.

38:49.520 --> 38:50.760
I'll get it for you, honey.

39:08.200 --> 39:09.600
Are you…

39:22.720 --> 39:25.640
JIANG YING

39:29.440 --> 39:30.320
Hello?

39:30.400 --> 39:32.320
I told you not to contact me anymore.

39:33.320 --> 39:35.280
Jiaxu, let's meet up.

39:35.360 --> 39:37.160
I called you, but you--

39:37.240 --> 39:38.120
I've told you.

39:38.200 --> 39:40.160
Let's not stay in touch anymore.

39:40.840 --> 39:43.080
So are you just going to abandon me?

39:43.160 --> 39:44.160
Duan Jiaxu.

39:45.040 --> 39:46.400
I'm busy. I'm hanging up.

39:58.720 --> 40:05.200
JIANG YING

40:15.160 --> 40:16.040
Do you want some more?

40:33.240 --> 40:34.280
Are you scared?

40:35.680 --> 40:37.720
No, I love this.

41:05.000 --> 41:06.040
I'm sorry.

41:06.120 --> 41:09.160
I didn't know you were afraid of chickens.

41:09.880 --> 41:10.720
It's okay.

41:11.640 --> 41:14.160
I'm not afraid of anything

41:14.240 --> 41:16.480
except for animals with sharp beaks.

41:17.920 --> 41:19.200
I see.

41:19.280 --> 41:20.800
It was really big.

41:26.400 --> 41:27.720
Do you need to wipe your sweat?

41:31.240 --> 41:32.520
I'll use the restroom.

41:32.600 --> 41:33.840
Okay.
